{"tid":1957502,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"公務員唔係condom","createTime":"2020-04-04T03:37:34.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-04T05:07:39.000Z","uid":153407,"like":21,"dislike":17,"uniUserReply":25,"replies":[{"pid":"a836a4ff90a03371056f431cbd634762a2a1fe79","tid":1957502,"uid":153407,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-04T03:37:34.000Z","msg":"近排見越來越多post批評公務員加人工<br />\n此風不可長<br />\n搞清楚事實先啦大家<br />\n今年三月個加人工，其實係上年4月1日應該加既人工黎架<br />\n上年香港運動，公務員默默忍受<br />\n大家上年加人工個陣，公務員係冇加人工，由得立法會未通過。<br />\n足足遲左成年，今年三月先通過<br />\n<br />\n而家想當公務員condom?<br />\n<br />\n公務員唔係condom"},{"pid":"c543ef4cc35db4a54c116c1787bb9b9e7de5b969","tid":1957502,"uid":126621,"like":3,"dislike":6,"score":-3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-04-04T03:39:48.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">1. 政府財赤</span></strong></span><br />\n減人工好合理姐<br />\n政府收支唔平衡唔通加人工？<br />\n成班都唔用腦<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">2.政府人工同私人市場無直接關係</span></span></strong><br />\n間公司賺定蝕先係最直接關係<br />\n唔好再打飛機話政府減薪<br />\n出面就減好撚多呢d 廢話<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">政府減唔減 出面已經減左</span><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">3.係政府限制左黑警同公務員同一個pool</span></span></strong><br />\n要加一齊加 要減一齊減<br />\n請矛頭直指捆綁式機制<br />\n而且係黑警搞到政府財赤<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\">4.減左50%=可請多一倍公務員</span></strong></span><br />\n減低失業率（多左17萬人就業）"},{"pid":"7013568bf18c1e13c2e264ff6c4c7db82d24057e","tid":1957502,"uid":153407,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"c543ef4cc35db4a54c116c1787bb9b9e7de5b969","tid":1957502,"uid":126621,"like":3,"dislike":6,"score":-3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-04-04T03:39:48.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">1. 政府財赤</span></strong></span><br />\n減人工好合理姐<br />\n政府收支唔平衡唔通加人工？<br />\n成班都唔用腦<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: re